# Amanda Natividad – Recent LinkedIn Posts Analysis

---

## Post 1

**Date:** 3 July 2026

**Topic:** AI visibility as a leading demand indicator

### Summary
Amanda explains that AI-generated recommendations are becoming an important indicator of future customer demand. Citing Similarweb research, she notes that brands appearing in AI-generated recommendations often experience increased branded search and direct website visits, even when AI referrals aren't directly measurable. She encourages marketers to evaluate how their brands are represented in AI tools by asking whether they appear in recommendations, are described accurately, are compared with the right competitors, and communicate compelling proof points.

### Main Takeaway
As AI increasingly influences buying decisions, marketers should monitor and optimize how their brands appear in AI-generated recommendations—not just traditional search rankings.

